Enumeration.label: Pad, filling and readying for launch

Parameter.name: apogee_from_ground
Parameter.LongDescription: Calculated on the FC in order to determine ejection.

Parameter.name: barometer_altitude_from_pad
Parameter.LongDescription: Initalized by the flight computer when it started or restarted.

Parameter.name: battery_voltage
Parameter.LongDescription: Current voltage of the FC battery

Parameter.name: fc_pressure
Parameter.LongDescription: Barometric pressure measured by the FC

Parameter.name: fc_rssi
Parameter.LongDescription: Relative Signal Strength Indicator of FC radio

Parameter.name: flight_stage
Parameter.LongDescription: The current stage the FC believes it is in.

Parameter.name: mov_hall_state
Parameter.LongDescription: Calculated from hall state sensor voltage.
